   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Year 1 of Imperator Caesar Marcus Aurelius Claudius Pius Felix Augustus, Phamenoth 5. ? has paid to Seuthos, praktor of the imposition in denarii and didrachmon, . . . into the account of Nilos, son of Ptollas and of the mother Ptolemais, an account of the didrachmon twelve drachmas, in total 12 drachmas; in the month of Pharmouthi he has equally  paid another twelve drachmas, in total 12 drachmas . . . "</ab>
         </div>
